{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_05_04",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 05 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんのお葬式が終わった後\n私は部屋に引きこもって、学校にも行かなくなった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After my sister's funeral\nI shut myself in my room and stopped going to school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.6418596268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.8551927884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃、渚は毎日うちに来てくれてたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ you came to my house every day‚ Nagisa‚ didn't you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8551927884,
      "endTime": 12.7398413976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 12.9465079785
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんのことが心配だったからね\nあんまり役には立たなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was because I was worried about you‚ Kotono\nI wasn't much help though",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9465079785,
      "endTime": 18.822653150500003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.0093197982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない！　私が立ち直れたのは渚のおかげよ\n渚がいなかったら私は今でも引きこもっていたかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true! It's thanks to you that I was able to get back on my feet.\nIf you hadn't been there‚ I might still be shut in…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0093197982,
      "endTime": 27.842970196499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.0496367296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな、大袈裟だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ that's an exaggeration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0496367296,
      "endTime": 30.3121763548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "大袈裟じゃないわ\n私は本当に、渚に救われたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not an exaggeration.\nI was truly saved by you‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0666666667,
      "endTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8399.999999999998,
          "startTime": 38.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.4521762372
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseroka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseroka-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.9141949814
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseroka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseroka-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.9141949814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、部屋にいるんでしょ？\n今日も学校に来なかったけど、まだ具合悪いの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ you're in your room‚ right?\nYou didn't come to school today either‚ are you still feeling sick?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9641949814,
      "endTime": 47.671020047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseroka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseroka-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.8843532086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "……声だけでも聞かせてくれたら安心するんだけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'd be relieved if you'd just let me hear your voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8843532086,
      "endTime": 59.5026982785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseroka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseroka-00-night",
      "startTime": 59.7093648117
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "……まだ話したくないか\nそうだよね、あんなことがあったばかりだもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You still don't want to talk‚ huh?\nI guess so‚ it was just after something like that happened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7093648117,
      "endTime": 68.5988433044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、私は帰るね\nまた来るから、今度は部屋に入れてくれたら嬉しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'm going home now.\nI'll come again‚ I'd be happy if you'd let me into your room next time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8121767521,
      "endTime": 77.0300906658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.2934241135
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.2934241135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "琴乃の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "琴乃の母",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktnmam001.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、琴乃の様子はどう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan‚ how's Kotono doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3434241135,
      "endTime": 82.77009590450001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "それが、部屋に閉じこもったまま\n顔も見せてくれなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ she's still holed up in her room\nand won't even show her face…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9767625331,
      "endTime": 88.9656062602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseliving-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.1522729555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私は琴乃ちゃんを諦めませんから\n毎日来て、何度でも琴乃ちゃんに話しかけます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I won't give up on Kotono.\nI'll come every day‚ and talk to Kotono as many times as it takes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1522729555,
      "endTime": 97.48404175430001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.6673746744
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.6673746744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "毎日、渚は放課後になるとうちに来て\n私の部屋の前で一方的に喋ってたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Every day‚ after school‚ Nagisa would come to my house\nand talk on and on in front of my room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.7173746744,
      "endTime": 107.4522272744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.6522271791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "学校で何があったとか\n近所に新しいお店が出来たとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened at school‚\nor that a new store had opened nearby‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6522271791,
      "endTime": 112.5656057039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私と一緒に何をやりたいとか\n一緒にどこへ行きたいかとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What she wanted to do with me‚\nor where she wanted to go with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.772272237,
      "endTime": 118.7175783475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.9109115759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "私が無視してもお構いなしで喋り続けて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when I ignored her‚ she kept talking on and on without a care…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9109115759,
      "endTime": 123.1589842478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 123.3589842955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、ちょっとしつこかったかな？\nそんな調子で一ヶ月くらい一人で喋り続けて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ was I a bit persistent?\nI kept talking by myself like that for about a month…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.3589842955,
      "endTime": 132.0605717818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "私が帰ろうとした時に、琴乃ちゃんがドアを開けて\n名前を呼んでくれた時は、嬉しくて泣いちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was about to go home‚ Kotono opened the door\nand called my name‚ I was so happy I cried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2672384103,
      "endTime": 140.36080034580002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.5608001551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "その日から琴乃ちゃんは私を部屋に入れてくれて\n少しずつ、顔を見ながら話すようになったんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From that day on‚ Kotono let me into her room\nand little by little‚ we started talking while looking at each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5608001551,
      "endTime": 149.3414119562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.5914117655
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagasektnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagasektnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.5914117655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、体調はどう？\nずっと休んでるけど、まだ学校に行くのは無理そう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ how are you feeling?\nYou've been resting this whole time‚ but does it still seem impossible to go to school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6414117655,
      "endTime": 160.04993704170002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
