      "text": "だから、手を繋いで笑い合う女の子を見て……\n私は独りじゃないんだって分かって、嬉しかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ seeing the girls holding hands and smiling…\nI knew that I wasn't alone‚ and I was happy.",
        "id": ""
